Package: getLattesHtml
Title: Parse Lattes Curriculum Vitae from HTML Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Francisco Pablo Huascar Aragão", "Pinheiro",
    email = "pablohuascar@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extracts structured data from CNPq Lattes curriculum vitae HTML
    files. The Brazilian government maintains an extensive base of curricula for
    academics across the country, documented in the 'Lattes' platform
    (<http://lattes.cnpq.br/>). This package parses HTML downloads of Lattes
    curricula and returns tidy tibbles suitable for batch processing with
    purrr::map() and purrr::list_rbind(). Covers personal data, education,
    professional activities, publications, advisorships, examination boards,
    and research projects.
